name.ja: <ruby>導<rt>みちび</rt></ruby>かれし<ruby>烙<rt>らく</rt></ruby><ruby>印<rt>いん</rt></ruby>

text.en: Once per turn, when your opponent activates a card or effect that targets 1 "Bystial" monster you control (and no other cards), or when your opponent activates a card or effect in response to your "Bystial" monster's effect activation: You can target 1 LIGHT or DARK monster in either GY; banish it, and if you do, negate that activated effect.
